stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (5 BREATHING TECHNIQUES FOR KIDS) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (1. BALLOON BREATH:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td (Breathe in through nose \(inflate your belly like a balloon\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (Breathe out through mouth slowly \(deflate the balloon\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (Repeat 5 times) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 624.0 Td (2. SQUARE BREATHING:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.0 Td (Breathe in for 4 counts | Hold for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.0 Td (Breathe out for 4 counts | Hold for 4 counts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.0 Td (Trace a square in the air while you do it) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 562.0 Td (3. FLOWER & CANDLE:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.0 Td (Smell the flower \(breathe in through nose\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.0 Td (Blow out the candle \(breathe out through mouth\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 514.0 Td (4. 5-4-3-2-1 GROUNDING:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 498.0 Td (5 things you SEE | 4 things you TOUCH) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 484.0 Td (3 things you HEAR | 2 things you SMELL | 1 thing you TASTE) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 466.0 Td (5. STARFISH BREATH:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 450.0 Td (Spread fingers like a starfish. Trace up each finger \(breathe in\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 436.0 Td (Trace down each finger \(breathe out\). 5 breaths total!) Tj ET
endstream
